# 接口名称: 获取 IP 信息
# 来源文档: spider_process.md
# 说明: 根据 `uid` 查询创作者/IP 基本信息。

@baseUrl = https://api.x-metash.cn

### 获取 IP 信息
POST {{baseUrl}}/h5/community/userHome
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "uid": "30",
  "fromType": "1"
}

### 示例响应
# {
#   "code": 200,
#   "data": {
#     "uid": 30,
#     "nickname": "故宫观唐",
#     "avatar": "...",
#     "description": "以故宫《石渠宝笈》著录历代书画为核心...",
#     "userType": 1
#   }
# }
